            <span class="text-3xl">üé•</span>
            Video Tutorials
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-4xl opacity-50">‚ñ∂Ô∏è</span>
            </div>
